5-15-2024 Changelog

Watchtower 2.1.1

Many major changes

Moved Ezra from KVM to bare metal for performance improvements and bug fixes

Node-to-node communication via custom /etc/hosts in Proxmox to prevent cascading failures in the future

New wt.local homepage

New Grafana dashboard

New VPN RADIUS monitoring functionality

New alert rule exceptions

New Prometheus Configuration to accomodate KVM to bare metal transition

Result of changes:


Improvements and maintenance 
